m x - \sum_{i=1}^m \alpha_{(i)} = 1
 x = \frac{1+\sum_{i=1}^m \alpha_{(i)}}{m} 
 \frac{1+\sum_{i=1}^m \alpha_{(i)}}{m} \geq \alpha_{(j)} \; , \; \forall j \in \{1,\ldots,m\} 
 \frac{1+\sum_{i=1}^m \alpha_{(i)}}{m} < \alpha_{(j)} \; , \; \forall j \in \{m+1,\ldots,n\} 
